  <brief_title>Safety and Tolerability of Omalizumab in Patients With Mild to Moderate Asthma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multi-center, Open-label, Multiple Dose Study in Mild to Moderate Asthmatics (With IgE/Body Weight Combinations Above That in the SmPC Dosing Table) to Determine Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics, and Pharmacodynamics of Omalizumab</official_title>
